## API Routes — AKTUAL LENGKAP

### `POST /api/auth/[...nextauth]` — NextAuth credentials
- Login dengan email + password
- Return session dengan `id`, `name`, `email`, `role`

### `GET /api/patients`
- Requires: session (any role)
- Returns: semua user dengan `role = PATIENT`, diurutkan alphabetically
- Select: `id, name, email, role, createdAt, _count.predictions`

### `POST /api/patients`
- Requires: session (any role)
- Body: `{ name, email, password }`
- Creates: user baru dengan `role = PATIENT` (password di-hash bcrypt)
- Returns: `{ id, name, email, role, createdAt }`

### `PUT /api/patients/[id]`
- Requires: session dengan `role = ADMIN`
- Body: `{ name, email }`
- Updates: nama dan email pasien (cek duplikat email)
- Returns: data pasien ter-update

### `DELETE /api/patients/[id]`
- Requires: session dengan `role = ADMIN`
- Action: hapus semua predictions pasien dulu (FK), lalu hapus user
- Returns: `{ success: true }`

### `GET /api/patients/[id]/history`
- Requires: session
- Returns: semua predictions pasien tertentu, urut `createdAt DESC`
- Select: semua field prediction (id, createdAt, result, probability, riskLabel, glucose, bmi, bloodPressure, age, pregnancies, insulin, skinThickness, diabetesPedigreeFunction, recommendation, glucoseSummary, bmiSummary, bloodPressureSummary, ageSummary)

### `POST /api/predict`
- Requires: session
- Body: `{ patientId, pregnancies, glucose, blood_pressure, skin_thickness, insulin, bmi, diabetes_pedigree_function, age }`
- Flow: forward ke Flask → simpan ke DB → return hasil
- Returns: `{ id, patientName, result, probability, risk_label, recommendation, clinical_summary }`

### `GET /api/history?page=1&limit=10&search=`
- Requires: session
- Returns: daftar pasien (PATIENT) yang sudah pernah skrining, paginated
- Format response:
```json
{
  "data": [{
    "id": 1,
    "name": "Siti Rahayu",
    "email": "siti@pasien.com",
    "totalScreenings": 3,
    "lastScreening": {
      "id": 12,
